title: The (Almost) Complete Intervention Collection
description:
The (ALMOST) Complete Collection of all the episodes of A&E's Intervention, spanning from seasons 1 (2005) to 14 (2013). There are some missing episodes, like Michael and Randi (Season 1) and Betsy (Season 3/4); so if you have any of the missing episodes, please let me know.
I ordered the episodes in accordance with wikipedia's ordering. If you're addicted to Intervention like I am, I hope you get your fix. Special thanks to timebuilding and everyone else that kept on seeding earlier episodes.
Happy seeding!

(Sorry about before! This torrent works and includes Jason/Joy!)
